<P>This would allow you to pre-buff an entire raid&nbsp;with Barkspur before engaging.&nbsp; An AE rampage mob could take over 90 thousand unresistable damage from Barkspur&nbsp;within seconds.&nbsp; Sorry, but this isn't going to happen.</P><BR>
