<P>Sure 90k if every&nbsp;silk class and priest class in the raid runs into melee range to get smacked.&nbsp; Last time i checked that seems like a pretty poor strategy to win.&nbsp; You figure thats about half your raid.&nbsp; So you could feesably do a 45k barkspur.&nbsp; Thats what 2&nbsp;mana burns? and its going to involve half your raid getting smacked 8 times by AE ramp which involves a risk of death.&nbsp; Also its going to involve a lot of cordination and time from multiple druids.&nbsp; Use of precious buff slots and be unusable on any raid with adds or no AE ramp.&nbsp; <BR></P>
<P>A couple AAs spent on 2 wizards has the same effect and it has much less risk and management involved to complete.&nbsp; I doubt by raid leader would even endorse such a tactic and probably laugh at me for suggesting it.&nbsp; In exchange this spell is now useful in groups - because right now i only use it for powerleveling.</P>
				
